The party said on Sunday it would not allow government s lack of rigour when proposing draft legislation to negatively affect the livelihoods of South Africans. We will continue to fight for a fair and constructive policy that provides more job opportunities and addresses social ills effectively. The DA will brief the media on in Johannesburg on Monday on what it views as the problematic aspects of the Draft Liquor Bill as well as the party s proposed amendments.TMG Digital